---
/* Homepage section divider — a 1px ink-black @ 12% hairline at content
   width. Sits between top-level sections so §01–§06 break visually
   without the heavy 1.5px ink rule each section used to draw
   individually. Subtle, uniform, decorative — role="presentation" keeps
   it out of the a11y tree.

   The earlier Concrete Gray version (#E6E1D8) sat at ~1.1:1 on Rice
   White — brand.md flags that combination as "effectively invisible."
   ink-black at 12% gives a quiet but actually-visible hairline on both
   surfaces the homepage uses (Rice White, White) without re-introducing
   the 1.5px chrome rule the V4 cleanup removed. */
---

<div class="section-divider" role="presentation">
  <span class="section-divider__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
</div>

<style>
  .section-divider {
    max-width: var(--content-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--gutter-mobile);
  }
  .section-divider__rule {
    display: block;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(21, 21, 21, 0.12);
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .section-divider {
      padding: 0 var(--gutter-desktop);
    }
  }
</style>
